{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/AlignmentID\/defaultValue(in:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"static","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"defaultValue","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"in","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"context","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore14ViewDimensionsV","text":"ViewDimensions","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewDimensions"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The context of the view that you apply","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the alignment guide to. The context gives you the view’s dimensions,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as well as the values of other alignment guides that apply to the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view, including both built-in and custom guides. You can use any of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these values, if helpful, to calculate the value for your custom","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"guide.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"context"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The offset of the guide from the origin in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s coordinate space."}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"ty